         <div xml:id="alalal-h80530"><!-- l4d20a9 -->
            <head xml:id="alalal-h80530-Hd1e99">Articulus 9</head>
            <head xml:id="alalal-h80530-Hd1e101" type="question-title">An horrendum fit incidere in manus
Dei ?</head>
            <p xml:id="alalal-h80530-d1e104">
               <cb ed="#Be" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="#Be" n="21"/>ARTICULUS IX.
<lb ed="#Be" n="22"/>An horrendum fit incidere in manus
<lb ed="#Be" n="23"/>Dei ?
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-h80530-d1e115">
               <lb ed="#Be" n="24"/>Deinde queritur de hoc quod dicit,
<lb ed="#Be" n="25"/>ibi, B, circa medium: <quote xml:id="alalal-h80530-Qd1e121"> Horrendum est
<lb ed="#Be" n="26"/>incidere, etc. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-h80530-d1e127">
               <lb ed="#Be" n="27"/>Contra :
<lb ed="#Be" n="28"/>Deus in infinitum est magis est 
mise<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="29"/>ricors, quam aliquis homo: ergo minus
<lb ed="#Be" n="30"/>horrendum est incidere in manus Dei,
<lb ed="#Be" n="31"/>quam in manus hominum: quia multae
<cb ed="#Be" n="c"/>
               <lb ed="#Be" n="32"/>sunt miserationes ejus: ergo videtur,
<lb ed="#Be" n="33"/>quod falsum dicat in Littera.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-h80530-d1e148">
               <lb ed="#Be" n="34"/>Soxutio. Dicendum quod, in opere 
mi<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="35"/>sericordie superexaltantis judicium, 
le<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="36"/>vius est incidere in manus Dei, quam in
<lb ed="#Be" n="37"/>manus hominis, hoc est, dum tempus
<lb ed="#Be" n="38"/>est miserendi et pcenitentie: dum au~
<lb ed="#Be" n="39"/>tem justitias judicabit in futuro, 
horren<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="40"/>dum est incidere in manus Dei magis
<lb ed="#Be" n="41"/>quam in manus hominis: quia tunc 
sic<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="42"/>ut dicitur, Proverb. vi, 34 et 33 : Zelus
<lb ed="#Be" n="43"/>et furor viri non parcet in die vindicte :
<lb ed="#Be" n="44"/>nec acquiescet cujusquam precibus, nec
<lb ed="#Be" n="45"/>suscipiet pro redemptione dona plurima.
<lb ed="#Be" n="46"/>Et per hoc patet solutio.
</p>
